property.description: House and lot are being sold as is and together with a total of 14.25 acres! Wonderful property minutes from the town of Sandy Creek, Sandy Pond, local campgrounds, snowmobile trails and Lake Ontario! Could be used as a seasonal cabin or updated into a cozy, year-round home. House needs some TLC, but the property is a must see! There is a beautiful creek that flows through the back of both lots. Included on the property is an attached garage and a large barn with fencing. Taxes and assessment are a combination of both the house with the lot and the vacant lot. Tax ID 355289-019-000-0001-017-040-0000 and Tax ID 355289-019-000-0001-017-080-0000. Don't miss this great opportunity!
